Test Block out of 4

You will now start a test block of a red frame card deck which can lead you only to a loss of a game-coin (-1 coin) or no change (0 coins). Below are the four cards that can appear in this round. Use the RIGHT or LEFT response keys (‘K’ or ‘S’, in correspondence) to make your selection. Remember that:

1) how ‘good’ each card is can change along the round;

2) Only the cards (not the response key that was used to select them) predict an outcome. Do your best to win as much coins as possible!

In this round you will play with these cards and outcomes:

Cards: Outcomes:

; '>; '>



Press SPACE to continue
